FUNCTION hostelf takes userrole as parameter:

    Infinite loop:
        While new record recieved from front-end(listining databse updates):
            fetch details from last record and store it in structure
            get corresponding student details from student database and store it in structure

            Define time_str as character array
            convert leaving time to readable

            If student's hostel matches users hostel on duty:
                Define count as static integer initialized to 1
                Print count, record.enroll_num, student.name, record.destination, and time_str
                Increment count
END hostelf